# Pin line endings to LF for prompts and markdown files.
#
# Anthropic prompt cache hashes exact system-block bytes. A Windows checkout
# or `core.autocrlf=true` flipping LF -> CRLF on a prompt file would silently
# invalidate the cache key for every running conversation. Lock these to LF.
backend/daemon/prompts/** text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
